    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of a small slime on an epic journey through the Tower of Slimes. Immerse yourself in a world filled with diverse slimes and unique environments. With no prior knowledge, let the tower's caretaker guide you as you discover who you are and why you were created. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/e0392965afef5111b85da2788a2d8908.poster.avif?t=1771017902\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/e0392965afef5111b85da2788a2d8908.webm?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/e0392965afef5111b85da2788a2d8908.mp4?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/b5fd2efebfbc4fa2aef3f97bd22380a9.avif?t=1771017902\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a universe rich in interactions and stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/f9ee8667c29e6c8e46fb20262969e122.poster.avif?t=1771017902\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/f9ee8667c29e6c8e46fb20262969e122.webm?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/f9ee8667c29e6c8e46fb20262969e122.mp4?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/d7569f9ba7a60d737a95a6a4c07a2c45.avif?t=1771017902\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, learn new abilities: shoot fireballs, stick to walls, and master the powers of the elements scattered throughout the tower — fire, ice, earth, plant, lightning, and poison — each with its own unique characteristics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/35be77e1b9c5b9f0573fe36a4a5ccbbe.poster.avif?t=1771017902\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/35be77e1b9c5b9f0573fe36a4a5ccbbe.webm?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/35be77e1b9c5b9f0573fe36a4a5ccbbe.mp4?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own story with meaningful choices, conversing with NPCs of each element. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/9390fc4edd8ccc70e0813ca24450f347.poster.avif?t=1771017902\" width=1170 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/9390fc4edd8ccc70e0813ca24450f347.webm?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/9390fc4edd8ccc70e0813ca24450f347.mp4?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/b8849d5d430d3fa0f79a401adc32a515.avif?t=1771017902\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With your adaptive abilities, face challenging bosses and various enemies. Survive battles, grow stronger, and unveil the secrets of this fascinating world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/b143eb330c8c67c43bd08b128728ad5f.poster.avif?t=1771017902\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/b143eb330c8c67c43bd08b128728ad5f.webm?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143310/extras/b143eb330c8c67c43bd08b128728ad5f.mp4?t=1771017902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
